    <item>
      <title>TPG 将减半对新 50 亿美元亚洲基金的中国投资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/tpg-will-halve-china-investments-in-new-5-billion-asia-fund</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据一位知情人士透露，TPG Inc. 即将关闭其第八只亚洲收购基金，规模约为 50 亿美元，新投资组合将把其在中国的配置比之前的区域基金削减一半以上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/tpg-will-halve-china-investments-in-new-5-billion-asia-fund</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 01:24:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国人民银行通过定盘发出强烈支持信号，人民币反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/yuan-edges-higher-as-pboc-sets-stronger-than-expected-fixing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在央行通过强于预期的每日参考利率表示对受管理货币的支持后，周五人民币收复跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/yuan-edges-higher-as-pboc-sets-stronger-than-expected-fixing</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 01:19:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚洲股市涨跌互现，中国支持人民币：市场总结</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-24/asian-shares-look-mixed-ahead-of-busy-data-week-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一早盘，亚洲股市窄幅波动，投资者期待本周繁忙的经济数据，包括美联储首选的通胀指标。在当局的支持下，人民币收复了周五的部分跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-24/asian-shares-look-mixed-ahead-of-busy-data-week-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 22:41:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>油价创历史新高，中石化2023年利润下降13%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-24/sinopec-2023-profit-falls-13-on-oil-prices-refining-record</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于油价下跌以及中国炼油厂的加工和进口创历史新高，中石化的年利润下降了 13%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-24/sinopec-2023-profit-falls-13-on-oil-prices-refining-record</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 08:39:13 GMT</pubDate>
